Summary: Reno NV 9/22/13 - Many ships - Amazing Video
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was the second night I noticed this star shape light ...that was larger than a star overlooking my neighborhood, above a hill. I could not see from street level, but shot many video's from 2nd floor window. It looked like many large ships and than smaller ones come across the screen. AMAZING. I included this short clip and have much more footage if your interested in looking into this further.
